properties.Zone_base: Area outside 2018 GNS Science worst case 2500 year inundation modelling from any source.
properties.Zone_expl: You do not have to evacuate this area after a long or strong earthquake or during an official tsunami warning.

properties.Zone_base: Zone includes sea, rivers, beaches, lagoons and estuaries.Evacuate zone after long or strong earthquake or in any official advisory or warning (of >0.3m wave height at coast)
properties.Zone_expl: The tsunami is unlikely to flood land but may cause strong currents/surges in the sea  stay out of the sea, estuaries and rivers, and off beaches after a long or strong earthquake or if you are told to in an official warning.

properties.Zone_base: Inland boundary based on 2018 GNS Science inundation modelling of worst case South American tsunami. Evacuate zone in official warning of >5m wave height at coast.
properties.Zone_expl: The tsunami is likely to flood a lot of land  you do not have to move out of this zone after a long or strong earthquake, you only need to move out of this zone if you are told to in an official warning.

properties.Zone_base: Inland boundary based on 2018 GNS Science inundation modelling of worst case southern Hikurangi tsunami. Evacuate zone after long or strong earthquake or official warning of 1-5m wave height at coast.
properties.Zone_expl: The tsunami is likely to flood some land  move out of this zone after a long or strong earthquake, or if you are told to in an official tsunami warning.
